      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready to get the job done? This vehicle is a fantastic option for anyone who values practicality and character! It has been a reliable companion and shows some honest signs of its journey, including typical cosmetic wear and tear. It remains a solid, functional choice for your daily needs and is priced to offer great value for its next owner!",
